{"tid":238931,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"[JJ屌地][食蟲]日本大學生表現愛地球的方式","createTime":"2017-05-11T10:34:04.000Z","updateTime":"2017-05-11T13:45:54.000Z","uid":75969,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"90b3bca1f2e2c0c6bf9a642eca1b0fb2bd3ccd31","tid":238931,"uid":75969,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-11T10:34:04.000Z","msg":"大家曾經做過什麼樣的努力愛地球呢？少開冷氣還是資源回收？日本大學生篠原祐太認為要以最直接的方式表達對大自然的愛意，因此他掏出GG插進土裡，如此就能感受到地球的柔軟與溫暖，卻讓指原莉乃與黑色美乃滋看得超傻眼！老實說最令本魚震驚的並不是他抽插地球又吃昆蟲，而是竟然有女朋友陪他一起幹這些事啊！！！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n餐餐食蟲<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z2i8L8v.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz2i8L8v.jpg&h=56c16451&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/q40L469.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fq40L469.jpg&h=8bd40f32&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o526qbW.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo526qbW.jpg&h=999145a4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n屌地<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Un51h97.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FUn51h97.jpg&h=a8c77a67&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n仲話射左想比攝影師睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n片<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IWfXHF3I-_8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIWfXHF3I-_8&d=NiOc6rc%2FE9fikVhzT7%2F1Gy7bS0i5kAixZS1hjGmvpwM%3D&h=b6c70506\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IWfXHF3I-_8</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁都有女 仲要成日打野戰<br />\n公平咩公平咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/o1kA1TH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fo1kA1TH.jpg&h=49e995a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nsource:<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.gamme.com.tw/1495914\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2